{"tid":1188681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驅趕公園大媽，你我岀一份力！關於遊樂場地條例","createTime":"2019-06-06T11:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T02:05:33.000Z","uid":160028,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f46cdefeac8497fdf16b05c6851b572a2e0feae0","tid":1188681,"uid":160028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"其實遊樂場地條例入面有一條條文關於:<br />\n<br />\n25.音樂及唱歌<br />\n除非署長已以書面准許操作或彈奏某種樂器，或利用某種樂器發出任何聲響，或唱歌，否則任何人不得在對任何其他使用遊樂場地的人造成煩擾的情況下，在遊樂場地內操作或彈奏任何樂器或其他器具(包括唱機或無線電器具)，或利用該等樂器或其他器具發出任何聲響，或唱歌。<br />\n<br />\n現時嘅弊處就無人願意作證上法庭作證檢控佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近睇新聞話康文署都諗住修例<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18區新聞/321545/康文署擬修例趕絕公園-大媽-噪音滋擾-目標今年7月通過審議\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F321545%2F%E5%BA%B7%E6%96%87%E7%BD%B2%E6%93%AC%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E8%B6%95%E7%B5%95%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD-%E5%99%AA%E9%9F%B3%E6%BB%8B%E6%93%BE-%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B47%E6%9C%88%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2Bgn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=46b802e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18區新聞/321545/康文署擬修例趕絕公園-大媽-噪音滋擾-目標今年7月通過審議</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家都可以一起關注下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52099bdd63436403fc9000f500394a37960fc65e","tid":1188681,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:37:29.000Z","msg":"係中國師奶，大媽係共產中文"},{"pid":"f6a0c41c002c69032578da8fec4cedb0a4817b7f","tid":1188681,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11d2b3953c664e616bee02426847552e289b718